snippet.title: Decocraft Spooky Update 2024
snippet.description:
Happy Halloween and Day of the Dead!
Grab the Decocraft spooky update for Minecraft Java Edition 1.16.5, 1.17.1 & 1.18.2

DOWNLOADS

Modrinth
https://modrinth.com/mod/decocraft/

Curseforge
https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/decocraft

CREDITS
Builders:
Momoko
Mimmichu
Mollusky
PaigeyPop

Cast:
Trick or Treater 1 - TheAnonymousGhoul
Trick or Treater 2 - PaigeyPop
Trailer Park Woman - Momoko
Pumpkin Man - DastardlyRed
Witch - Mollusky

Music from #Uppbeat
https://uppbeat.io/t/monument-music/halloween-town
License code: EIIVE1PLGLJ0MMXY
